title: WLAB Tech
description: Kick off your next, great Gatsby project with this default-starter-intl. This barebones starter ships with the main Gatsby configuration files you might need.
author: @wiziple
index_about_text: WLAB is one of the e-cigarette brands under WLAB (Shenzhen) Technology Co., Ltd., and a cutting-edge design brand of domestic e-vaporized cigarettes. The company is dedicated to R&D, design, production, sales and wholesale of consumer-grade electric atomizers and their derivatives. Driven by user experience, it integrates high-end aesthetic design and world-leading art technology.
